    <item>
      <title>棉花价格上涨，因交易商平仓对风暴和产量风险的看跌押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/cotton-jumps-as-traders-cover-bearish-bets-on-storm-output-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[棉花期货出现自 2 月份以来的最大涨幅，因为恶劣的天气风险和较低的产量前景导致交易商平仓看跌押注，从而推高了价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/cotton-jumps-as-traders-cover-bearish-bets-on-storm-output-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 17:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储押注导致美元下跌，新兴市场资产上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/emerging-market-currencies-gain-as-dollar-extends-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员预期美联储本周将实施四年来首次降息，新兴市场资产周一小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/emerging-market-currencies-gain-as-dollar-extends-slide</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 10:19:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险交易员在美联储降息前买入新兴市场债券 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/emerging-market-etfs-fall-for-2nd-week-in-289-7-mln-streak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者乐观地认为，本周备受期待的美联储降息将推动发展中国家债券市场上涨，投资者周五纷纷将资金投入购买新兴市场债券的交易所交易基金 (ETF)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/emerging-market-etfs-fall-for-2nd-week-in-289-7-mln-streak</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 10:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
